{"tid":1787732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［打擊人血饅頭］觀塘成業街100outlet 賣Pepe 人血饅頭兼侮辱女手足","createTime":"2019-12-18T06:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T00:53:00.000Z","uid":196031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e82ac6b0d9c2aaf7c80b784cf99a5c593e75c5","tid":1787732,"uid":196031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n成業街新開左間濕鳩100 outlet 正門擺着大大隻Pepe 公仔，明目張膽食緊人血饅頭。<br />\n<br />\n有女手足睇唔過眼話同職員理論話侵犯版權，點知幾個廢佬職員同埋一個又黑又矮嘅男職員圍攻。個男人仲要瘋狂用粗口侮辱女手足。<br />\n<br />\n大家如果行過見到鋪頭仲擺住pepe公仔嘅記得多多支持下呢間新鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n千祈要阻止暴徒裝修佢哋同埋貼街招唱衰佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uD6CcuU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuD6CcuU.png&h=1247b292&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa8f0cee2610aa5024e243d6b2ee6de3836d3ff4","tid":1787732,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"52c9e9a6a2ef43bdd92c8f98f09c25d37384cf3d","tid":1787732,"uid":23672,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"其實點解賣Pepe 公仔=人血饅頭? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f913172a9595e8efa4df04ba8a654b34a141ce88","tid":1787732,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T00:53:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1786535/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1786535/page/1</a><br />\n呢D先係血饅頭"}]}